    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. Suspension components remain tight, providing excellent lateral load management and communicative steering feedback. This is a mechanically sorted enthusiast machine that balances raw performance with daily usability.",
