      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is the perfect blend of performance and reliability. Finished in a sophisticated Charcoal Metallic, the exterior retains a high-gloss shine, though it shows a few honest stone chips from highway commuting. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring premium leather seating with only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every button, switch, and sensor functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system. Mechanically, this car has been meticulously cared for, with a documented history of synthetic oil changes and a recent full brake service. It shifts smoothly and pulls strong, offering a tight, responsive driving experience. It is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
