      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque delivery across the powerband. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to a variable M differential lock. Recent mechanical attention includes a cooling system refresh and subframe inspection to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension retains its precision with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration, delivering the communicative hydraulic steering feedback this chassis is renowned for. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains potent and the throttle response is razor-sharp, making it an ideal candidate for the spirited driver.",
